{"tid":1476795,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"根本港幣換美金就冇得輸","createTime":"2019-08-16T02:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T02:51:14.000Z","uid":241006,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2ad49cce2a66063a7da5426daa0f572528a9a462","tid":1476795,"uid":241006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:33:10.000Z","msg":"香港行聯繫匯率<br />\n港幣 美元價就喺7.8上下浮動<br />\n用港幣兌美金除咗手續費之外<br />\n根本可能最儘蝕得一千幾百<br />\n如果兌得少<br />\n可能一餐lunch(當然你兌十億八億咁我收聲）<br />\n但一旦香港有事<br />\n港幣出事<br />\n美金就係最大保障<br />\n你買保險都唔止呢小小錢啦<br />\n依家係香港政府包底 匯率波動唔大<br />\n所以應該一出糧就換美金（除咗必須用嘅港幣消費外）<br />\n儲蓄應該玩美元儲蓄"},{"pid":"e235f11bd36d567ed75c3840c8c46a846a16fed7","tid":1476795,"uid":241006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:33:28.000Z","msg":"利申 文科9up"},{"pid":"d94047bb7fec937c70d14f71f4c89da9c7737f3b","tid":1476795,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:33:57.000Z","msg":"無地方洗呢"},{"pid":"9a112c67a2bd3bb0d7c5591a7b4b5af22c60a830","tid":1476795,"uid":241006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:34:02.000Z","msg":"有冇經濟專家入來分享下"},{"pid":"8b1daa22ab66aac4be41949865cb56df5b6ae4a3","tid":1476795,"uid":241006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d94047bb7fec937c70d14f71f4c89da9c7737f3b","tid":1476795,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:33:57.000Z","msg":"無地方洗呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:36:00.000Z","msg":"很多人做港元定期<br />\n其實轉美金做美元定期都得<br />\n麻煩小小嘖<br />\n我覺得唔一定要用美元代替港幣消費<br />\n但揸一半美金安全好多"},{"pid":"56b15540a840b70607266035e6f47463aebbcf24","tid":1476795,"uid":164761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff86e128ef27a918c859a1c160b2b6b65b00b76d","tid":1476795,"uid":8081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,